  "about_item": [
    "Luxury & Fashion-Forward Pet Purse: Designed for stylish women, this dog purse carrier features an elegant straw-woven body with PU leather trim. Looks like a chic handbag while discreetly carrying your small pet",
    "Designed for Small Pets: Size: 14.17'' L x 7.09''W x 8.66''H. Roomy enough for comfort without looking bulky, so it stays stylish on the go. Recommended for small dogs & cats up to 10bs. Suitable breeds include: Chihuahua, Yorkie, Pomeranian, Maltese, Toy Poodle, Shih Tzu puppy, and similar-sized pets",
    "Lightweight & Comfortable to Carry: Made from lightweight straw woven material with soft PU handles, this pet purse reduces shoulder strain and stays comfortable even during long trips. Soft-sided structure fits under most airline seats - TSA approved. Ideal for flights, vet visits, shopping,travel or daily outings. Please check with your airline before purchase to confirm size requirements",
    "Breathable & Comfort: Top & Side mesh ventilation window improves airflow to keep pets cool, relaxed, and a removable padded bottom that adds comfort and support while allowing easy cleaning after travel or daily use. Built-In Safety Leash help prevent your pet from jumping out",
    "Practical Storage & Gift-Ready Choice: A convenient side pocket keeps essentials like your phone, keys, or treats within easy reach. With its stylish look and thoughtful details, this pet purse makes a beautiful gift for dog or cat lovers"
  ],
