        "title": "Pet Carrier Purse for Small Dogs and Cats",
        "text": "This pet carrier is more like a stylish purse than a traditional carrier bag. It looks beautiful, matches outfits easily, and is practical for taking a small dog or cat anywhere. The inside is soft, and there is also room for essentials like a wallet and phone thanks to a side pocket. Your pet can be secured with the attached leash and zipper closure, while the front opening allows them to keep their head out comfortably. It also has a small window that can be opened or closed. The straw-style design with leather accents looks very attractive, and the size is great for a small dog or cat at 14 inches long and a little over 8 inches tall.",
